Shows errors, warnings, and other inspection highlights inline. Simply install the plugin and inspection descriptions will appear on the right side of the lines. Each severity has a different color, with support for both light and dark themes.

Supported languages: Java, XML Developed for developers by developers, it enables you to: Instantly transform bad code to good code with expert recipes written by Secure Code Warrior’s in-house secure coding developers and architects - with years of collective experience in cybersecurity Release code faster as you do not need to wait for scans to finish or issues to surface during code review or pull requests
